headline: Got $200? 2 Dividend Stocks to Buy and Hold Forever
summary: Medtronic is a medical device powerhouse closing in on Dividend King status.  Merck is a high-yield pharmaceutical giant with a dividend that has trended generally higher over time.  If you don't specialize in the medical space, you should probably avoid small, research-driven healthcare stocks.
